Zimbabwe â€™s central bank approved
$1.5 billion in foreign credit lines this year sourced by local
banks,  Reuters  reported, citing  Reserve Bank  of Zimbabwe
Governor Gideon Gono.  Lenders, which need central bank approval to negotiate
